    "title": "Marketplace Manager - Titan Eyeplus Global Group - Growth Opportunity",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Titan Eyeplus Global Group. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Marketplace Manager to strengthen our Pune-based team.\n\nAbout Titan Eyeplus Global Group:\nTitan Eyeplus Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Any graduate with relevant experience\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Titan Eyeplus Global Group!",
